form.text:
Store at room temperature
in a sealed plastic bag
(We recommend eating
within 1-2 days)

Place the bread in a zippered
plastic bag and freeze it.
(Can be stored up to 2 weeks)

Defrost naturally for 30-60 minutes at room temperature,
then toast in the oven or air fryer and enjoy.
Tastes best when spritzed with 
a little moisture and oven-roasted.

If you don't have an oven or air fryer, naturally defrost for 30-60 minutes at room temperature and then gently toast for 1-2 minutes per side
in a heated frying pan or toaster and enjoy.

Miri Bread is free of preservatives and oxidants and contains natural enzymes so it's tastier and easier to digest. So please eat it before its best before date and eat it quickly once the bag has been opened!

How to store &
how to enjoy Miri Bread
